@NODE MAIN "Disaster Master"

     Name         : Disaster Master V2

     Aliases      : No Aliases

     Clone        : No Clones

     Type/size    : File/1740

     Symptoms     : Shows an alert

     Discovered   : 10-10-90

     Way to infect: File infection

     Rating       : Less Dangerous

     Kickstarts   : 1.2/1.3/2.0

     Manifestation: Pretend to be a cls-command

     Removal      : Delete file. (c/cls)

     Comments     : After starting the virus stays resident by
                    using the Kick-vectors. On the next reset
                    the virus patches the OpenWindow()-Vector from
                    the intuition.library. If you are now booting
                    with a unprotected disk (or HD), the virus copies it-
                    self into the C: directory with the name CLS and
                    modifies the startup-sequence with "CLS *".
                    The star (*) after CLS has the following meaning:

                    If you are starting the virus with CLS, it clears
                    the CLI-window. But if you are starting the virus
                    by typing CLS * it doesn`t clears the CLI-Window.

                    This was made because the user shouldn`t wonder why
                    suddenly the CLI-window is cleared on every boot.
                    Depending of infections, the virus gives out an 
                    alert:

                    Software Failure. Press left mouse button to continue
                    Guru Meditation #00000002.06001989

                    After pressing any mouse button another alert appeares

                    Incoming special-message.
                         Your Amiga is infected by DISASTER-MASTER V2 !!!
                         probably the virus created by mankind....
                         Left = continue        Right = self destruction

                    Click  on this gadget to see a @{" Demo " SYSTEM V-IFF:Disastermaster} of the Disaster 
                    Master virus. Click left mouse button to return.

                    If you are pressing the right mouse button the virus
                    jumps to a endless-routine by showing some colors:

            ENDLESS:
                    MOVE.W $DFF006,$DFF180
                    BRA.S  ENDLESS

                    You must reset your Amiga!!!
                    It exists a trojan which installs this virus:
                    Intro-Maker by TCR - please look there.
 
A.D 12-93
